text: Super Muñeco (Super Doll) (10 April 1962 – 9 February 2022) was a Mexican Luchador enmascarado, or masked professional wrestler. Super Muñeco is Spanish for "Super Toy". Super Muñeco was best known for having the second highest number of Luchas de Apuestas. His real name was unknown. He died in Mexico City on 9 February 2022, at the age of 59. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Mexican professional wrestlers Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
title: Super Muñeco
